; Regression test for issue #834: --pedantic doesn't work if specified in Ledger file
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/834
;
; When --pedantic is placed in the journal file itself, it should enforce
; strict checking of accounts, just as it does when given on the command line.

--pedantic

commodity $
    format $1,000.00

account Expenses:Food
account Assets:Cash

2024/01/01 Declared accounts
    Expenses:Food       $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Undeclared account
    Expenses:Unknown    $5.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 20:
While parsing posting:
  Expenses:Unknown    $5.00

Error: Unknown account 'Expenses:Unknown'
end test
